The AI assistant for                     ,
not copy-pasters.

MindToPaper is an essay assistant that doesn't write for you but empowers you to write better. It guides students through the entire essay-writing process, making it easier and more efficient without taking away the learning experience.
Choose from predefined essay formats and fill in tailored sections to build a cohesive essay.
Polish your writing with a personalized word bank for clearer and more impactful communication.
Turn your thoughts into organized flowcharts for a clear and structured brainstorming process.
Users can select their desired essay format, such as TEEL or Argumentative, from a convenient dropdown menu. Based on their choice, the website generates tailored input forms for each section.

Once all inputs are completed, they are seamlessly merged into a single editable text box, presenting a clear essay preview for final adjustments. This intuitive system ensures users can efficiently structure and refine their essays with ease.
